The practical details of the legal procedings against <a class=glossary href="/glossary.html#corrupter">the corrupter</a>
are unimportant.  When journalists dwell on those, they are <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/apr/06/media-coverage-trump-arrest-2016-repeat">playing
